  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::TutorialStep
  id: draft02
  text: "COST:\nEach Dialogue Card has a Confidence Cost to play. With the exception
    of \u201CDance,\u201D that cost is displayed on the card. \n\nMore expensive
    cards are more difficult for Luke to say, and are usually riskier in how they\u2019ll
    be received by Daisy.\n\nBRANCHES:\nLuke\u2019s Confidence level also affects
    HOW his words come out,\nand Luke\u2019s words affect how Daisy responds."
  boxSize: {x: 600, y: 300}
  boxAnchoredPosition: {x: 0, y: 0}
  dismissMode: 0
  showBackdrop: 1
